Si ka duwan SARS, bukaanno badan oo qaba MERS waxay sidoo kale horumariyaan cillad kelyaha oo daran, taas oo ilaa hadda lagu arkay kaliya cudurada ay keento HCoVs.
In ka badan 30% bukaanada waxay qabaan calaamado caloosha ah sida shuban iyo matag.
Laga bilaabo Febraayo 14, 2020, in ka badan 2500 kiis oo la baaro ayaa la soo sheegay iyadoo heerka dhimashada ay sarreyso 34.4%, taas oo ka dhigaysa MERS-CoV mid ka mid ah fayrasyada ugu waxyeellada badan ee loo yaqaan aadanaha.
