Taariikhda cudurrada faafa: (1) Taariikhda safarka ama deganaanshaha magaalada Wuhan iyo aagagga ku xeeran, ama bulshooyinka kale ee lagu soo warramey kiisaska COVID-19 14-kii maalmood ee la soo dhaafay ka hor inta aan calaamaduhu bilaaban; (2) Taariikhda la xiriirka kiisaska faafa ee SARS-CoV-2 (oo ay weheliso baaritaanka nucleic acid-ka oo wanaagsan); (3) Taariikhda la xiriirka bukaannada qaba qandho ama calaamadaha neefsashada ee magaalada Wuhan iyo aagagga ku xeeran, ama bulshooyinka kale ee lagu soo warramey COVID-19 14-kii maalmood ee la soo dhaafay ka hor inta aan calaamaduhu bilaaban; (4) Taariikhda la xiriirka kooxda kiisaska la xaqiijiyay (xaalado feyrar ah oo ≥ 2 ah iyo/ama calaamadaha neefsashada oo ka dhacay gudaha 2 toddobaad meelaha yaryar sida guryaha, xafiisyada, dugsiyada, iwm.).
Tilmaamaha caafimaad: (1) qandho iyo/ama calaamado neefsashada; (2) oo leh astaamo ka tarjumaya cudurka COVID-19; (3) tirada unugyada dhiigga cad ee guud waxay muujineysaa lymphocyte caadi ah, hoos u dhac ama hoos u dhac.
Aqoonsiga kiiska la xaqiijiyay waa inuu ku saleysan yahay kiis shaki ah oo leh hal shay oo ah cudur-dhaliye ama caddayn serum oo ah: (1) tijaabo PCR-ga waqtiga dhabta ah ee SARS-CoV-2 oo soo noqnoqda; (2) isku-duwidda guud ee hidde-wadaha fayraska oo muujinaya isku-dhafnaan sare oo ka badan noocyada cusub ee loo yaqaan 'coronavirus'; (3) tijaabooyinka serum-ka ee ku saabsan SARS-CoV-2 ee ku saabsan IgM-ga gaarka ah iyo IgG-ga gaarka ah; ama SARS-CoV-2-ga gaarka ah IgG-ga gaarka ah ee ka soo noqnoqda diidmada, ama isbeddelka ka soo noqoshada diidmada, ama qiyaasta faa'iidada caafimaad ee ka sarreysa ≥ 4 jeer marka loo eego marxaladda degdegga ah.
