Angiotensin -modifying enzyme 2 (ACE2) waa enzyme la xidhiidha dusha sare ee unugyada (magdhowga unugyada) ee sanbabada, xididdada, wadnaha, kelyaha iyo mindhicirka.
ACE2 waxay dheellitirtaa firfircoonaanta enzyme-ka angiotensin-modifying enzyme (ACE) ee la xiriira iyadoo la yareynayo xaddiga angiotensin-II iyo kor u qaadista angiotensin (1-7), taasoo ka dhigaysa bartilmaameed daroogo oo rajo leh daaweynta cudurada wadnaha. ACE2 waxay sidoo kale u adeegtaa sidii barta gelitaanka unugyada loogu talagalay qaar ka mid ah coronaviruses.
Nooca aadanaha ee enzyme waxaa badanaa loo yaqaan hACE2.
Angiotensin -ka - bedelaya enzyme 2 waa metallogen oo ku jira zinc oo ku jira gudaha iyo dusha sare ee unugyada kale.
ACE2 wuxuu leeyahay N - terminal peptidase M2 domain iyo C - terminal electrin adrenal amino acid carrier domain.
ACE2 waa nooc ka mid ah borotiinka qanjirka I oo leh domain-ka firfircoon ee enzymatically aan la shaacin ee ku yaal dusha sare ee unugyada sanbabada iyo unugyada kale.
Qaybta ka baxsan unugyada ee ACE2 waxaa burburiya enzyme kale oo la yiraahdo Shadese, waxaana ka dhasha borotiinka lagu kala diri karo ee dhiiga ku jira, ugu dambeynna waxaa lagu tuuraa kaadida.
