Tilmaamaha kale ee cilmi baarista waxaa ka mid ah horumarinta tallaalka COVID-19 iyo bedelka plasma ee la xiriira faa'iidooyinka caafimaadka. SARS-CoV-2 wuxuu leeyahay qiyaastii 66 borotiin oo bartilmaameed ah, mid walbana wuxuu leeyahay dhowr goobood oo ku xirnaanta ligand.
Falanqaynta goobaha xidhitaanka waxay bixisaa qorshe sax ah oo lagu horumarinayo daawooyinka ka hortagga fayraska ee wax ku oolka ah ee ka hortagga borotiinnada COVID-19.
Badeecadaha ugu muhiimsan ee SARS-CoV-2 waa protease-ka papane-ka, RNA-ku xiran RNA polymerase, helixase, S protein iyo ADP ribosphate.
