18-kii Maarso, WHO waxay ku dhawaaqday in chloroquine iyo hydroxychloroquine la xiriira ay ka mid noqon doonaan afarta daawo ee lagu baranayo qeyb ka mid ah tijaabooyinka caafimaad ee Solidarity.
Guddoomiyaha New York Andrew Cuomo ayaa ku dhawaaqay in tijaabooyinka New York State ee chloroquine iyo hydroxychloroquine ay bilaaban doonaan 24-ka Maarso. Bishii Maarso 28, FDA waxay oggolaatay isticmaalka hydroxychloroquine sulfate iyo chloroquyl phosphate oo hoos imanaya Awoodda Isticmaalka Degdegga ah (EUA).
Daaweynta looma oggola FDA nidaamka tijaabada caafimaad waxaana loo oggol yahay EUA oo keliya sida daaweynta tijaabada ah ee loogu talagalay isticmaalka degdegga ah ee bukaannada isbitaalka la dhigay laakiin aan awoodin inay helaan daaweynta tijaabada caafimaad.
CDC waxay sheegtay in "Isticmaalka, qiyaasta ama muddada loo isticmaalo hydroxychloroquine ee ka hortagga ama daaweynta cudurka SARS-CoV-2 aan wali la dhisin".
