Tallaalka COVID-19 waa tallaal la malaynayo oo ka hortaga cudurka Coronavirus Disease 2019 (COVID-19).
Inkastoo aysan jirin mid ka mid ah tallaallada oo dhammaystiray tijaabooyinka caafimaad, haddana waxaa jira dadaalo badan oo lagu horumarinayo tallaal noocaas ah.
Dhamaadkii Febraayo 2020, Ururka Caafimaadka Adduunka (WHO) wuxuu sheegay in aan la fileynin in tallaal laga helo SARS-CoV-2, fayraska cudurka keena, in ka yar 18 bilood.
Shan ka mid ah musharraxiinta tallaalka ayaa ku jiray daraasadaha badbaadada ee wajiga 1aad bishii Abriil.
COVID-19 waxaa la ogaaday bishii Diseembar 2019.
Caafimaadka ayaa kor u kacay sanadka 2020, taasoo keentay maalgashi ballaaran iyo howlo cilmi baaris oo lagu horumarinayo tallaalka.
Ururo badan ayaa adeegsanaya hiddo-wadaha la daabacay si loo horumariyo tallaalada laga yaabo inay ka difaacaan SARS-CoV-2.
Bishii Abriil, waxa lagama maarmaanka u ah dadaalka CEPI ee horumarinta tallaalka ayaa ah xawaare, awoodda wax soo saarka, qorsheynta ballaaran iyo helitaanka caalamiga ah.
Bishii Abriil, saynisyahannada CEPI waxay ku wargeliyeen in 10 barxad teknoolojiyad oo kaladuwan ay ku hoos jireen cilmi baarista iyo horumarinta intii lagu jiray bilowgii 2020 si loo abuuro tallaal wax ku ool ah oo looga hortago COVID-19.
Bartilmaameedyada ugu muhiimsan ee la hormariyey ee daraasadaha amniga ee marxaladda I waxaa ka mid ah:
Aashida Nukliyeerka (DNA iyo RNA) (Fasalada I ee horumarinta iyo musharaxa tallaalka: Moderna, mRNA-1273)
Fayraska fayraska (wax -abuuraha heerka 1aad iyo musharaxa tallaalka: CanSino Biologics, fayraska adenovirus nooca 5aad)
Sida ay ku wargeliyeen saynisyahannada CEPI bishii Abriil, 115 oo ka mid ah musharraxiinta tallaalka ayaa ku jira marxaladda horudhaca ah ee horumarinta, 78 ka mid ah ayaa la xaqiijiyay inay yihiin mashaariic firfircoon (79 sida laga soo xigtay Machadka Milken), 37 kalena waa la shaaciyay, laakiin macluumaad yar oo dadweyne ayaa la heli karaa (oo la naqshadeynayo ama la qorsheynayo).
Tijaabooyinka wajiga I -II waxaa lagu sameeyaa tijaabooyinka badbaadada iyo difaaca bilowga ah, waxaa badanaa lagu sameeyaa si aan kala sooc lahayn, placebo - kontorool ah iyo goobo badan, iyadoo la dejinayo qiyaaso sax ah oo wax ku ool ah.
Tijaabooyinka wajiga III waxay inta badan ku lug leeyihiin ka qaybgalayaal badan, oo ay ku jiraan koox xakameyn ah oo la kormeero saameynta xun ee qiyaasta ugu fiican, iyo tijaabinta waxtarka tallaalka ee ka hortagga cudurka.
79 ka mid ah musharraxiinta tallaalka ee horumarinta firfircoon (oo la xaqiijiyay bilowgii Abriil 2020), 74 weli ma aysan kujirin qiimeynta aadanaha (wali waxay ku jireen cilmi baaris "preclinical").
Qiyaastii 24 Janaayo 2020 gudaha Australia, Jaamacadda Queensland ayaa ku dhawaaqday inay baarayaan suurtagalnimada tallaal molikal ah oo si hidde-wadaha ah wax uga beddelaya borotiinka fayraska si uu kiciyo jawaabta difaaca.
Qiyaastii 24 Janaayo 2020 gudaha Kanada, Xarunta Caalamiga ah ee Tallaalka ee Jaamacadda Saskatchewan (VIDO-InterVac) waxay ku dhawaaqday inay bilaabeen shaqada tallaal, iyagoo ujeedadoodu tahay inay bilaabaan tijaabooyinka aadanaha sanadka 2021.
Mashruucyada horumarinta tallaalka waxaa lagu dhawaaqay 26 -ka Janaayo 2020 Xarunta Xakamaynta iyo Kahortagga Cudurrada ee Shiinaha iyo 28 -ka Janaayo 2020 Jaamacadda Hong Kong.
Qiyaastii 29 Janaayo 2020, shirkadda dawooyinka ee Yansen oo uu hogaaminayo Henneke Schutemaker ayaa ku dhawaaqday inay bilowday inay horumariso tallaal.
